{"tid":1623163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港革命第六大訴求 廢除緊急法","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T18:57:40.000Z","uid":124891,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"74af86edb15fa5c058ba4a2c9fd614067082436b","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:43:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第六大訴求 : 廢除《緊急法》<br />\n6th Demand : Abolish Emergency Regulations Ordinance</span></span><br />\n<br />\n三權分立乃香港法治體制的基石，<br />\n司法 立法 行政 本應相互制衡，<br />\n《基本法》列明行政長官和行政機關受立法會和司法機關的監督，<br />\n立法會本身亦受司法機關的監督。<br />\n任何立法程序理應建基於互相制衡之原則，<br />\n《緊急法》令香港三權分立的制度名存實亡，<br />\n賦予行政長官越過立法部門立法的能力，<br />\n其能力於《緊急法》下凌駕其餘兩權。<br />\n長久以來執行的立法機制被完全架空，<br />\n此舉無疑嚴重害香港之法治，<br />\n而且給予政府繞過立法會打壓異見的權力，<br />\n令香港的自由危在旦夕。<br />\n故香港市民 要求政府立即廢除《緊急法》。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n香港特區政府"},{"pid":"4fe7f2eb5d854876bff84ed833c52531bd8535e9","tid":1623163,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:44:12.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08b64ab2754bf609b65396a1a1988b393ea57e4d","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:46:33.000Z","msg":"今次只係試水溫<br />\n接受左下次一定唔止禁蒙面咁簡單<br />\n治本方法只有廢除"},{"pid":"015a791ef6f4c02e4426105dd64e695a723c5251","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:48:32.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"2d7ed70359dfea7bdbc55d6df5ad44ea85924ebd","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:49:38.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"cc932d8ae19974b0e16f871d9df28e2f5980e843","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:49:48.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3054055666c12eab2093ef35bcfbec00b9c51523","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:50:05.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8d3493926be3fff8a9334c471c3562a70d18cee4","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:50:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"481f229a6d6f8011eb5b10160641fe628d699a97","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:50:57.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"f20a1cb8956142656e1dd0f12ff1982471cc796c","tid":1623163,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:51:14.000Z","msg":"仆街林鄭成日話修例係要維護法治 大家有眼見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb3631f31152af5b316909ec477614f2b73ae49","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:51:47.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"5b5eefce0f6b15fa5a0095b4ccd018c844427eec","tid":1623163,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:51:48.000Z","msg":"其實一個訴求就夠，馬上雙普選<br />\n<br />\n之後咩訴求都可以實現"},{"pid":"8d2080ab7be18d12fb758c27023d3022a815f148","tid":1623163,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:53:47.000Z","msg":"廢你老母<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>成立臨時政府 香港獨立!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"58fc39e195cc2f29cf64466139a4264faa43b012","tid":1623163,"uid":228701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:54:17.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n五大訴求已成過去<br />\n香港人不再乞求中共施捨<br />\n<br />\n驅逐共黨<br />\n光復香港"},{"pid":"fe7b8509f0c60f7136276da982e8a079d3ae2483","tid":1623163,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:54:22.000Z","msg":"唔好麻木 希望大家明白緊急法唔單單係禁蒙面咁簡單"},{"pid":"b5029f181f23696a8ab77fd7057fe25ea046b0a5","tid":1623163,"uid":185999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20